<table border="0" cellpadding="8">
<tr><td colspan="2"><p>Please read <a href="article.fod_IssueId_25_ArticleId_1498">Where Have All The Witches Gone</a> and <a href="article.fod_IssueId_25_ArticleId_1491">Group Discussion</a> before completing this questionnaire.</p>
<p>All replies are strictly anonymous.</p>
</td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">1.</td>
<td valign="top">Are you male or female?<br>
<textarea name="q_1" rows="5" cols="58"></textarea></td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">2.</td>
<td valign="top">Have you ever seriously played a persona of the opposite gender? If so, why did you chose to play a persona of the opposite gender?<br>
<textarea name="q_2" rows="5" cols="58"></textarea></td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">3.</td>
<td valign="top">Did anyone realise? If so, what do you think gave it away?<br>
<textarea name="q_3" rows="5" cols="58"></textarea></td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">4.</td>
<td valign="top">How do you feel about people role-playing an opposite gender persona?<br>
<textarea name="q_4" rows="5" cols="58"></textarea></td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">5.</td>
<td valign="top">If you are female, have you ever experienced any overt sexism? What happened and what did you do?<br>
<textarea name="q_5" rows="5" cols="58"></textarea></td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">6.</td>
<td valign="top">If you are male have you ever witnessed any overt sexism towards a female player? What happened and what did you do?<br>
<textarea name="q_6" rows="5" cols="58"></textarea></td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">7.</td>
<td valign="top">If you are male, have you ever knowingly been overtly sexist as either a joke or seriously? If so, what happened?<br>
<textarea name="q_7" rows="5" cols="58"></textarea></td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">8.</td>
<td valign="top">As a male persona, have you ever experienced any overt sexism?<br>
<textarea name="q_8" rows="5" cols="58"></textarea></td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">9.</td>
<td valign="top">Regardless of your gender would you consider yourself sexist in any way?<br>
<textarea name="q_9" rows="5" cols="58"></textarea></td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">10.</td>
<td valign="top">If you see a newbie, would you react differently to them if they had either an obvious male or female name? How would you react in each case?<br>
<textarea name="q_10" rows="5" cols="58"></textarea></td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">11.</td>
<td valign="top">Do you think that female players have an easier time? Give examples.<br>
<textarea name="q_11" rows="5" cols="58"></textarea></td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">12.</td>
<td valign="top">Do you think that female players have a harder or easier time wizrunning? Give examples.<br>
<textarea name="q_12" rows="5" cols="58"></textarea></td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">13.</td>
<td valign="top">Out of the 36 wizzes there are 4 witches. Do you think that this is a low, high or reasonable ratio?<br>
<textarea name="q_13" rows="5" cols="58"></textarea></td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">14.</td>
<td valign="top">If you think that this is a low ratio why do you think that this is the case?<br>
<textarea name="q_14" rows="5" cols="58"></textarea></td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">15.</td>
<td valign="top">Do you perceive there to be any difference between a wizard and witch?<br>
<textarea name="q_15" rows="5" cols="58"></textarea></td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">16.</td>
<td valign="top">Do you treat a witch differently to a wizard? Give examples.<br>
<textarea name="q_16" rows="5" cols="58"></textarea></td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">17.</td>
<td valign="top">Have you experienced or witnessed any unwelcome obscene behaviour towards a female player?<br>
<textarea name="q_17" rows="5" cols="58"></textarea></td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">18.</td>
<td valign="top">Have you experienced or witnessed any unwelcome obscene behaviour towards a male player?<br>
<textarea name="q_18" rows="5" cols="58"></textarea></td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">19.</td>
<td valign="top">If you are a male player, do you sometimes find it hard interacting with female players?<br>
<textarea name="q_19" rows="5" cols="58"></textarea></td></tr>
<tr><td align="right" valign="top">20.</td>
